<plot>The Pink Panther takes his camera to the wood, intending to shot animal pictures, but the forest creatures prove as uncooperative as with shooting hunters. A woodpecker systematically cuts off any branch the panther sits on, a frog lures him to the voracious teeth of an alligator, a butterfly onto a log drifting to a high cliff, wasps are their nasty stinging selves. Even when the plagued panther decides to shoot a flower instead, another local makes his all too characteristic mark on the set...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?433336</url></doc>
